Reach
[i]Charging Thunder[/i] – Whenever a creature you control attacks, put a charge counter on Tailtiu, Thunder Noble. At the beginning of your end step, you may remove any number of charge counters from Tailtiu. If you do, she deals damage to target creature equal to the number of counters removed this way. Excess damage is dealt to that creatures controller.
Promoted Class – {W}{B}
